                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <desc>
                    The presence of work by both the “red box artist” and the “partial margin artist” may indicate either collaboration or close proximity in one shop
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#ir(ecto) #109v #110r #110v" facs="001 111 112">Fols. ir(ecto), 109v, 110r, 110v</locus>
