                    <desc>
                    Numbered quires: quires 4–10 and 12
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a">
                    <desc>
                      Scribal intervention:
                      words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#1r #39r #42v #48v" facs="002 040 044 050">folss. 1r, 39r, 42v, 48v, </locus>, etc.);
                      lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#101r" facs="102">101r, </locus>);
                      erasure markings are visible (<locus target="#77r" facs="078">77r, </locus>);
                      text has been removed (e.g., <locus target="#51v" facs="053">51v</locus>)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                  </list>
